                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070701-61-off375 t18070701-61-cd376"></join>, one hundred wine glasses, value 50 s. twenty glass decanters, value 10 s. a deal box, value 1 s. a pair of snuffers, value 6 d. and two copper boilers, value 1 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070701-61-victim655" type="victimName">
